oracle.xml.parser.v2

Class XMLDocumentFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.xml.parser.v2.XMLNode
      • oracle.xml.parser.v2.XMLNSNode
        • oracle.xml.parser.v2.XMLElement
          • oracle.xml.parser.v2.XMLDocumentFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, NSResolver, NSName, DocumentFragment, Element, EventTarget, Node, ElementEditVAL, NodeEditVAL

     
    public class XMLDocumentFragment
extends XMLElement
implements DocumentFragment, java.io.Externalizable
    This class implements the DOM interface for DocumentFragment. It extends XMLElement rather than XMLNode so it can be handled as an element. This is convenient in processing.
    See Also:
    DocumentFragment, NodeFactory, DOMParser.setNodeFactory(oracle.xml.parser.v2.NodeFactory), Serialized Form
